on keeping kids healthy
and out of the E.R.

00:42.833 --> 00:46.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LINDA NEUHAUSER, University
of California, Berkeley: In
Alameda County alone, we might

00:46.633 --> 00:51.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
