President (through
translator): We never
interfere into political

01:37.500 --> 01:42.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
lives and political processes
in other countries, and
we would very much like
that nobody interfered

01:42.466 --> 01:45.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
into our political life and into
the political life in Russia.

01:45.833 --> 01:49.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
