in the internal political
struggle in the U.S.

01:49.633 --> 01:54.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Meanwhile,
Hillary Clinton said today
that Putin certainly interfered

01:54.033 --> 01:57.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
