Trump and defeat her.

01:57.000 --> 02:02.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
U.S. intelligence agencies and
the Congress are investigating
whether the Russians coordinated

02:03.133 --> 02:05.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
