from both sides of the aisle
to deliver a budget that funds

03:06.700 --> 03:10.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the rebuilding of the United
States military, makes historic
investments in border security,

03:12.433 --> 03:17.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
