would be a bad idea.

03:56.233 --> 04:01.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
A guilty plea today from
a white former policeman
who shot a black man
to death in Charleston,

04:02.133 --> 04:04.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
South Carolina.

04:04.266 --> 04:08.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
