on murder charges, but, today,
Slager pleaded to federal civil

04:15.700 --> 04:17.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
rights violations.

04:17.366 --> 04:20.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Under the deal, the state
agreed to drop its murder case.

04:20.600 --> 04:22.800 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
No sentencing date was set.

04:22.800 --> 04:27.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
