50:08.733 --> 50:12.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: You know,
throughout, it is this strange
mix of insecure, very human man,

50:14.200 --> 50:15.866 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
