tortured individual.

51:07.666 --> 51:11.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So,
thin-skinned, media-hating.

51:11.000 --> 51:16.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Soon as your book came
out, there were some
obvious comparisons...

51:16.000 --> 51:17.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JOHN A. FARRELL:
Yes, us as the enemy.

51:17.000 --> 51:18.666 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

51:18.666 --> 51:19.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
