51:19.466 --> 51:20.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN A. FARRELL: Yes.

51:20.433 --> 51:21.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

51:21.933 --> 51:22.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But how far
