51:37.633 --> 51:42.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He actually wrote books and he
was -- had a basic reverence,
despite what he did in

51:43.866 --> 51:47.500 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Watergate, for the
institution of the presidency.

51:47.500 --> 51:52.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
When he lied, he expected that
you would believe him, whereas,
Trump, I get the idea sometimes

51:54.066 --> 51:58.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
