rubbing it in your face.

52:01.533 --> 52:04.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So, those are, I think,
major differences
between the two of them.

52:04.866 --> 52:09.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
